Please ensure that you have a JPG image named `coffee-beans-background.jpg` in the `public` directory of your Next.js project.

The image should adhere to the following specifications:

- File Type: JPG
- Dimensions: 1920x1080 pixels
- Resolution: 72 DPI
- Content: A pattern or close-up shot of coffee beans.
- Color Scheme: Browns and creams, aligning with the Coffee World aesthetic.
- Responsive Behavior: The image will be used with `background-size: cover;` in CSS to scale proportionally and cover the entire background.